parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag sensor can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to a risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The passenger airbag light remains illuminated
the "Service Airbag" message appears on the instrument panel
the passenger airbag is disabled
and the airbag system may not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The temporary recall fix for the passenger airbag sensor failure may not be a permanent solution, leading to repeated failures and increased risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The passenger airbag light remains illuminated
the "Service Airbag" message appears on the instrument panel
and the airbag system may not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The airbag system malfunction can cause the airbag system to deploy unnecessarily or not deploy at all in the event of an accident, leading to a risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light remains illuminated
the "Service Airbag" message appears on the instrument panel
and the airbag system may deploy unnecessarily or not deploy at all in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Faulty Air Bag Sensor in Seats
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The faulty air bag sensor in the seats can cause the airbag system to malfunction, potentially leading to failure to deploy in the event of a crash, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The "Service Air Bag" light illuminates
the airbag system malfunctions
the passenger side seat airbag may not deploy
the airbag system may not function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Ignition and Start Switch Recall Parts Issue
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The ignition and start switch recall parts issue can cause delays in repairs, leaving vehicles in an unsafe condition, which can lead to accidents or other safety issues.
symptoms: Dealerships are unable to obtain recall parts
repairs are delayed
vehicles are left in an unsafe condition.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inadequate illumination of the instrument cluster can make it difficult for drivers to read essential information, such as speed, during daytime driving, which can compromise vehicle safety and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Difficulty reading gauges
especially the speedometer
during daytime driving
inadequate illumination of the instrument cluster
gauges appear dark or dimly lit
inability to read gauges without straining.
